{
  "stem": "17543.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 101.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I know for sure, somehow or other, in spite of that crowd, I, I had just the feeling she was coming on the same way that I was going that turned to the left, and I'm quite sure I heard the next one have to turn to the left as well.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was quite sure my mother was somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it so fast was going on, I couldn't see among the people I had to hurry up, go, and then nonstop they was [INAUDIBLE] schnell, schnell.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This means fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think is that mean.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And had to keep going fast, fast.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had to keep move on, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was really frightened, because these soldiers had the weapon under their arm.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And people told me who was understand German-- so you see, all age understand German in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in school had to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Before I was old enough to learn German language, they went to school, they learned the German language.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they said, they are not going to be afraid to use it, if not doing as told, so just do what is told.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway when, when we came out of this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, got this rag-- and we all had to go to the barrack number where they was telling us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There every barrack was absolutely jam-packed with women.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I haven't seen any young or old ones.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the youngest are seen, it's sort of like me and older, but still young.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now this barrack I went in there was all, most of them was young girls.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they all was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was just going crazy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went out of that barrack and went one barrack to the other to the other.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
